!* (all but the 0th)
!:n (n-th component)
!:$ (last component)
!:^ (first component)
!command
<sub>:h (head of sub)
<sub>:t (tail of sub)
<sub>:r (remove .xxx part from substitution)
<sub>:q (quotes)
<sub>:x (break into space separated words and quote)
Redirect stderr to stdout 2>&1
Redirect stdout to stderr 1>&2
set -euo pipefail
https://www.gnu.org/software/bash/manual/html_node/Shell-Parameter-Expansion.html
${parameter#word} begin remove shortest word
${parameter##word} begin remove longest word
${parameter%word} trailing remove shortest word
${parameter%%word} trailing remove longest word
